WEBVTT

00:00:00.760 --> 00:00:02.800
"How much pain medication are you taking?"

00:00:04.120 --> 00:00:06.960
That was the very routine question
that changed my life.

00:00:07.880 --> 00:00:09.376
It was July 2015,

00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:11.776
about two months after
I nearly lost my foot

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:13.400
in a serious motorcycle accident.

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:16.896
So I was back in my orthopedic
surgeon's office

00:00:16.920 --> 00:00:18.920
for yet another follow-up appointment.

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:20.936
I looked at my wife, Sadiye;

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.200
we did some calculating.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.360
"About 115 milligrams
oxycodone," I responded.

00:00:26.960 --> 00:00:28.616
"Maybe more."

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:32.695
I was nonchalant, having given
this information to many doctors